---
Scaffold per-project .agent/ store and register it with the daemon

Usage: init [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --quiet
          Suppress non-essential output (state.json, .gitignore, registry, disclosure)

      --uninstall-project
          Remove this project's entry from ~/.agent/registry.toml and exit. Does not delete the project's .agent/ store

  -h, --help
          Print help
